-- Pernod-Ricard Sells Lindauer and New Zealand Wine Brands For $65 Million
-- B y   C l e m e n t i n e   F l e t c h e r
-- 2010-10-18T06:00:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/pernod-ricard-sells-lindauer-and-new-zealand-wine-brands-for-65-million.html
Pernod-Ricard SA announced today the
sale of its Lindauer “and several other New Zealand wine
brands” to a group of buyers made up of Lion Nathan New Zealand
and Indevin for 88 million New Zealand dollars, or about 47
million euros, the company said today in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Clementine Fletcher at 
 cfletcher5@bloomberg.net  